{"author":"Claude","data":{"alias":"plot-home-gob","assignee":"claude","description":"## Why\n\n`docs/import-export.md` honestly notes that bulk import takes one git commit and\none lock per event, so multi-thousand-ticket imports serialize the write lock and\ncan take minutes. But there is no consolidated **scale envelope** telling\nadopters what the tool can take: how many tickets/events/clones, expected\nlist/search latency, git object growth, and the maintenance commands that keep a\nlong-lived store healthy. Popularity changes the load profile (Jira imports,\nbulk migrations, many agents, multi-year stores), and adopters need honest\nnumbers to plan.\n\n## What\n\nAdd `docs/scale-envelope.md` documenting, with **representative measured\nnumbers** produced by a quick local benchmark run during implementation:\n\n- Ticket / event / clone counts the design comfortably supports.\n- Import throughput (events/sec) and the per-event commit+lock cost.\n- `list` / `search` / replay latency at a few representative store sizes.\n- Git object / pack growth expectations on a long-lived `tickets` branch, and\n  why `gc.auto=0` is set.\n- Compaction thresholds and the recommended maintenance commands\n  (`compact` / `compact-all` / `fsck`).\n\n## Scope\n\nOne doc (`docs/scale-envelope.md`) + a short reproducible measurement method.\nDocs-only: no batched-commit import and no CI benchmark harness (both OUT per the\nepic). Cross-link from README and `docs/import-export.md`.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] `docs/scale-envelope.md` exists with representative measured numbers for\n  counts, import throughput, and list/search latency.\n- [ ] It documents git-growth expectations and the compaction/maintenance\n  commands.\n- [ ] The measurement method is reproducible (documented commands/store sizes).\n- [ ] README and `docs/import-export.md` link to it; no benchmark harness is\n  wired into CI.","id":"d063-90d1-1c60-4f0a","parent_id":"b02d-10bc-07ee-49e7","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"story","title":"Publish a scale-envelope doc with representative measured numbers"},"env_id":"58e9f32e-f999-436d-9c1a-5d0eef5c9903","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1783148932495149440,"uuid":"bc939640-c2e7-4481-bbfe-37533e678a98"}